andial&amp;author=B+Reichwage&amp;author=M+Levy&amp;author=V+Duenas&amp;author=L+Sturdivan&amp;publication_year=2008&amp;journal=Neurosurgery&amp;pages=472-480&amp;doi=10.1227%2F01.neu.0000316015.05550.7a&amp;pmid=18382326">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">8.</div><div id="r8" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Humphrey C, Kumaratilake J. Ballistics and anatomical modelling: a review. <em>Leg Med (Tokyo)</em> 2016;23(21):29.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Ballistics+and+anatomical+modelling%3A+a+review&amp;author=C+Humphrey&amp;author=J+Kumaratilake&amp;publication_year=2016&amp;journal=Leg+Med+%28Tokyo%29&amp;pages=29">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">9.</div><div id="r9" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Powers DB, Delo RI. Characteristics of ballistic and blast injuries. <em>Atlas Oral Maxillofac Surg Clin North Am</em> 2013;21(1):15–24.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.cxom.2012.12.001">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23498328/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Characteristics+of+ballistic+and+blast+injuries&amp;author=DB+Powers&amp;author=RI+Delo&amp;publication_year=2013&amp;journal=Atlas+Oral+Maxillofac+Surg+Clin+North+Am&amp;pages=15-24&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.cxom.2012.12.001&amp;pmid=23498328">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">10.</div><div id="r10" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Hanna TN, Shuaib W, Han T, Mehta A, Khosa F. Firearms, bullets, a