 role of computed tomography in terminal ballistic analysis. <em>Int J Legal Med</em> 2008;122(1):1–5.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s00414-006-0145-3">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17205351/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=The+role+of+computed+tomography+in+terminal+ballistic+analysis&amp;author=GN+Rutty&amp;author=P+Boyce&amp;author=CE+Robinson&amp;author=AJ+Jeffery&amp;author=B+Morgan&amp;publication_year=2008&amp;journal=Int+J+Legal+Med&amp;pages=1-5&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs00414-006-0145-3&amp;pmid=17205351">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">13.</div><div id="r13" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Bolliger SA, Thali MJ, Bolliger MJ, Kneubuehl BP. Gunshot energy transfer profile in ballistic gelatine, determined with computed tomography using the total crack length method. <em>Int J Legal Med</em> 2010;124(6):613–616.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s00414-010-0503-z">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20725735/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Gunshot+energy+transfer+profile+in+ballistic+gelatine%2C+determined+with+computed+tomography+using+the+total+crack+length+method&amp;author=SA+Bolliger&amp;author=MJ+Thali&amp;author=MJ+Bolliger&amp;author=BP+Kneubuehl&amp;publication_year=2010&amp;journal=Int+J+Legal+Med&amp;pages=613-616&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs00414-010-0503-z&amp;pmid=20725735">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">14.</div><div id="r14" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div clas